    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんにちは！　雨の中でもこうやって\n待っていただいて、本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello everyone! Thank you so much\nfor waiting‚ even in this rain!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 10303.3333333,
          "startTime": 15.07
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私以外のメンバーですが\nごめんなさい、実は雨で到着が遅れているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for the other members‚\nI'm sorry‚ but they're delayed due to the rain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-03.m4a",
          "delay": 13276.6666667,
          "startTime": 24.71
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 16.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "四人が着くまで後十五分ほどあるんですが……\n良かったらそれまで、私の歌を聴いてくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are 15 minutes left until the other four arrive……\nIf you don't mind‚ would you like to listen to my song until then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 25.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "わっ……ふふ、ありがとうございます\nこんなに喜んでもらえて、私も嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…… Hehe‚ thank you.\nit makes me happy to see you're all so pleased!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 34.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "短い時間ではありますが、私の歌……聴いて下さい\n『未来模様』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it's a short time‚ please listen to my song…\n『Future Signs』",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 43.6999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（どうなることかと思ったが、琴乃の歌が、曇っていた）\n（お客さん達を照らして、笑顔にしてくれた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was worried about what would happen‚ but Kotono's song brightened）\n（gloomy atmosphere of the audience‚ and made them smile…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ずぶ濡れになりながらも、ファンのために歌う……）\n（琴乃の想いが伝わってくる……いいステージだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Singing for the fans even while getting soaked…）\n（Kotono's feelings are being conveyed… What a great performance.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 61
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-03.m4a",
          "delay": 12466.666666600006,
          "startTime": 67.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 60.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございました。ソロで二曲\nお届けしましたが……楽しんでもらえましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much. I've just performed\ntwo songs by myself… Did you enjoy them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 68.500004069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nさて、そろそろ……あ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nWell then‚ it's about time… Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、大変お待たせしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ thank you for waiting so long!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 77.9666692097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ここからは、今度こそ私達五人の――\n月のテンペストのステージをお届けします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From here on‚ finally‚ it's time for the five of us—\nto take the stage of Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.766670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽フェスの翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Day After the Music Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4000025431,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3292642999963,
          "startTime": 87.1333318074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7000086228
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7000086228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\n……くしゅん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.\n……Ah-choo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.866670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か？　昨日は雨でかなり濡れたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay? You got soaked in the rain yesterday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2666697184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ。念のため今朝は熱も測りましたし\n今日はこれからすぐMV撮影に向かうんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm okay. Just in case‚ I took my temperature this morning‚\nWe're heading straight to the music video shoot now‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが、先方に相談して\n撮影開始まで少し時間を作ってもらったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that‚ I talked to the shooting staff‚\nand they gave us a little extra time before the shoot starts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.233336385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　時間を……って、どうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Extra time… What for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.233336385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈のお墓参りをしたいと言ってただろ？　せっかく\nだから、月ストのみんなで行ったらどうかと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you wanted to visit Mana's grave‚ right? Since this is\na rare opportunity‚ I thought‚ we can all go together with Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.566670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3000030517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この間言ったこと、覚えててくれたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… You remembered what I said the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、ずらした時間もそれほど長くない\n少し急ぐが、大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we don’t have much extra time‚\nso we'll have to hurry a bit‚ is that alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7666697184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n……ありがとうございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\n…Thank you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.5166768391
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.5166768391
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん。私……BIG4になれたよ\nお姉ちゃんだったら、とっくになってたのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big sister. I… became BIG4.\nIf it were you‚ would you have already reached that point a long time ago?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「ふっふっふ、来るのがおそーい！」\nなんて言いそうだな、麻奈だったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Fu fu fu‚ you're late!\"\nI think Mana would say like that.",
        "id": ""
