      "text": "……お姉ちゃん、私ね\n昨日、雨の中で一人でステージに立ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Big sister‚ you know‚\nyesterday‚ I stood on stage alone in the rain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.766674296,
      "sfxList": []
