    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの時みたいに晴れたりはしなかったけど\nそれでも、ファンのみんなは温かく迎えてくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It didn’t clear up like it did when you performed in the rain‚\nbut everyone welcomed me warmly.",
        "id": ""
