      "text": "それにね、私一人の時は晴れなかったけど\n五人揃って歌ったら……いつの間にか晴れてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's more‚ the weather wasn't sunny when I was alone‚\nbut when all five of us sang together… it cleared up before I knew it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.7666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
