      "text": "私達が五人揃えば、雨だって吹き飛ばせるんだって\nそう思ったら……なんだか、凄く嬉しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that if we are together‚ we can even blow away the rain.\nWhen I thought about that… Somehow‚ I felt so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.4666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
