      "text": "（ひたむきに前へ進み続けている、というか）\n（……人気がさらに高まってるのも納得だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's like she keeps single-mindedly moving forward.）\n（……It's no wonder she is getting more popular.）",
        "id": ""
